long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Добавляет кнопки в календарь нетологии для экспорта в календарь Google

This extension adds google calendar buttons to https://netology.ru/ that let you export events into your own personal google calendar. Netology is an education portal. Exported information is just the event title and a link to netology.
